sentence: Wednesday's session closes with the NASDAQ Composite Index at 6,025.23.
The total shares traded for the NASDAQ was over 2.11 billion.
Advancers stocks led declining by 1.62 to 1 ratio.
There were 1772 advancers and 1091 decliners for the day.
On the NASDAQ Stock Exchange 130 stocks reached a 52 week high and 16 those reaching lows totaled.
The most active, advancers, decliners, unusual volume and most active by dollar volume can be monitored intraday on the Most Active Stocks page.
The NASDAQ 100 index closed down -.13% for the day; a total of -7.1 points.
Seagate Technology PLC ( STX ) had the largest percent change down (-16.83%) while Wynn Resorts, Limited ( WYNN ) had the largest percent change gain rising 5.9%.
The Dow Jones index closed down -.1% for the day; a total of -21.03 points.
Procter & Gamble Company (The) ( PG ) had the largest percent change down (-2.51%) while Verizon Communications Inc. ( VZ ) had the largest percent change gain rising 1.41%.
